ษอออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออป
บ                     The Sysops Tale                                     บ
บ                                                                         บ
บ               BBSing is so much fun,                                    บ
บ               I did it all the time,                                    บ
บ               so I thought I'd start a bbs,                             บ
บ               that was just for me and mine.                            บ
บ                                                                         บ
บ               The first week was really great,                          บ
บ               new callers I was meeting,                                บ
บ               and reading lots of great new mail,                       บ
บ               and passing out my greetings.                             บ
บ                                                                         บ
บ               The second week was almost fun,                           บ
บ               the message base was growing,                             บ
บ               the files were going up and down,                         บ
บ               things were smoothly flowing.                             บ
บ                                                                         บ
บ               The third week was OK I think,                            บ
บ               a few problems here and there,                            บ
บ               but so far I had only gained,                             บ
บ               a very few gray hairs.                                    บ
บ                                                                         บ
บ               The first month was over now,                             บ
บ               the board was still on-line,                              บ
บ               but folks had started writing me,                         บ
บ               and answers took so much time,                            บ
บ                                                                         บ
บ               And after that it got so busy,                            บ
บ               with all that mail to do,                                 บ
บ               I wished I had the time and cash,                         บ
บ               to hire an extra crew.                                    บ
บ                                                                         บ
บ               The messages were growing now,                            บ
บ               the mail was piling up,                                   บ
บ               I barely had sufficient time,                             บ
บ               to fill my coffee cup.                                    บ
บ                                                                         บ
บ               The doors started going down,                             บ
บ               the modem overheated,                                     บ
บ               the hard disk crashed and lost my files,                  บ
บ               and I just felt defeated.                                 บ
บ                                                                         บ
บ               But this stuff is so much fun,                            บ
บ               I really can't stop now,                                  บ
บ               I'll cut and paste it back on-line,                       บ
บ               and make it work somehow.                                 บ
บ                                                                         บ
บ               And now I'm so much wiser,                                บ
บ               I'll never let it fail,                                   บ
บ               for now I'll just have to go,                             บ
บ               and answer all my mail.                                   บ
บ                                                                         บ
บ               Copyright (c) 1992, John Chambers                         บ
